Project: contextshift — CLI tool and Node.js library that translates AI context files between tools (CLAUDE.md, AGENTS.md, SOUL.md, .cursorrules, copilot-instructions.md, .windsurfrules, GEMINI.md, cowork-instructions.md). Zero dependencies.


Commands:
  node test/index.test.js (run the test suite (custom harness, no framework))
  npx contextshift CLAUDE.md --to cursor --dry-run (test a translation without writing files)